Constructor Detail

FileTypeFilter

public FileTypeFilter()
Creates an instance of the FileTypeFilter class to filter File objects based on type, which is determined by their extension. By default, any File object with the specified file types, stored in the fileTypes Set object, are accepted.

FileTypeFilter

public FileTypeFilter(boolean inclusive)
Creates an instance of the FileTypeFilter class to filter File objects based on type, which is determined by their extension. File objects will be included if the inclusive parameter is true and the File objects type is a member of the fileTypes Set object, excluded otherwise.
Parameters:
inclusive - is a boolean value indicating true if File objects having a file type contained by this filter are accepted or rejected.
